name: 明快 CrispMix
description:
这个CKPT主要强调一种明快清爽的画风，比起油画和厚涂类模型，表现阴影的色块面积较为控制，画面整洁干净，非常适合例图中时尚服装的展示。

注意：

特别感谢zakp无私分享的的LoRA模型 fashion girl 使我得到了这样的画面效果，由于这个CKPT已经融合了fashion girl，请不要再在使用过程中再次添加，否则会造成过拟合

PS：这个CKPT是我尝试了不少次的融合配方，得名于乐事薯片，V1.0是黄瓜味（取名障碍的我一直是看见啥取啥的

This CKPT mainly emphasizes a bright and refreshing painting style. Compared to oil painting and thick paint models, it controls the area of the color blocks that represent shadows, making the picture clean and neat. It is very suitable for showcasing fashion clothing in example images.

NOTE:

Special thanks to zakp for sharing the LoRA model "fashion girl" selflessly, which has enabled me to achieve this kind of visual effect. Since this CKPT has already incorporated the LoRA, please do not add it again during use, otherwise it may cause overfitting.

P.S: This CKPT is the result of multiple attempts at fusion, and it's named after the Lay's potato chips flavor, v1.0 "cucumber" v1.1 “lime” (I have a naming disorder and always name things based on what I see : ) ).
